---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Dev Logs | Phoenix Vector">
  <main class="devlog-page">
    <section class="devlog-hero">
      <h1>Dev Logs</h1>
      <p>
        Development notes, build updates, design changes, and behind-the-scenes
        progress from Mind Arc Games.
      </p>
    </section>

<section class="devlog-grid" aria-label="Phoenix Vector development logs">
    <article class="devlog-card">
    <p class="devlog-meta">v0.1.1 • Profile / Energy Update</p>

    <h2>Profile & Energy Systems</h2>

    <p>
      A foundational update focused on first-time player setup, persistent progression data,
      mission energy usage, and internal testing stability.
    </p>

    <a href="/phoenixvector/devlog/v0-1-1/" class="devlog-link">
      Read Log
    </a>
  </article>
  <article class="devlog-card">
    <p class="devlog-meta">v0.2.0 • UI / Bug Fix</p>

    <h2>N.T.D.C. Interface Overhaul</h2>

    <p>
      A visual redesign pass focused on establishing the new N.T.D.C. interface language,
      including menu styling, button treatment, and a fix for the start button flash issue.
    </p>

    <a href="/phoenixvector/devlog/v0-2-0/" class="devlog-link">
      Read Log
    </a>
  </article>


</section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .devlog-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #081120 0%, #040814 55%, #02050d 100%);
    color: #dbe7f5;
  }

  .devlog-hero {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: #f8fbff;
  }

  p {
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
    max-width: 720px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #9fb2c9;
  }

  .devlog-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
}

.devlog-card {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 200, 87, 0.22);
  border-radius: 20px;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255, 200, 87, 0.12), transparent 34%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.92), rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.96));
  box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
}

.log-date {
  margin: -0.35rem 0 1rem;
  color: rgba(248, 251, 255, 0.68);
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.devlog-meta {
  margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #ffc857;
}

.devlog-card h2 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #f8fbff;
}

.devlog-card p {
  margin: 1rem 0 0;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: #c7d2df;
}

.devlog-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  align-self: flex-end;
  margin-top: auto;
  padding: 0.85rem 1.15rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: #ffc857;
  color: #111;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition:
    transform 0.2s ease,
    box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.devlog-link:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(255, 200, 87, 0.28);
}
</style>
